Package nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.processing

This package contains interfaces for components that can process DataParticels (Fetchers, Batchers and Operations) and MetaParticles (MetaParticleHandler).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Batcher
    An interface describing the batch functionality: to collect one or more particles in a batch based on a certain criteria.
    Fetcher
    A Fetcher retrieves data from a specific source.
    MetaParticleHandler
    An object must implement this interface to become a handler for a specific type of MetaParticle.
    Operation
    An operation performs the processing of particles in a fieldGroupValue.
    ParticleBatchOperation
    A ParticleBatchOperation performs the processing of particles in a DataParticleBatch, which is produced by a Batcher.
    SingleParticleOperation
    A SingleParticleOperation performs the processing of individual DataParticles.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BatcherException
    Special type of Exception for when an error occurs in the batching process.
    OperationException
    Special type of Exception for when an error occurs in the Operation.
